quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  7,105,"jdyr bi'ana laa 'aqul ealaa allah 'iilaa alhq, whry bi 'ana altzmh, qad jitukum bbrhan whjt bahrt min rabikum ealaa sidq ma 'adhkurah lkm, fatlq -ya frewn- maei bani 'iisrayiyl min 'asrk wqahrk, wkhll sabilahum lebadt allh"
  7,106,"qal frern lmwsa: 'iin knt jyt biayat hsb zemk fatny bha, wahdrha endy; ltshh dewak wayuthbit sdqk, 'iin kunt sadqana fima addaeyt 'anak rasul rabi alealmyn"
  7,107,"falqa musaa esah, fthwlt hyat ezymt zahirat lleyan"
  7,108,"wjdhb yadah min jybh 'aw min jnahh fa'iidha hi bayda' kallbn min ghyr brs ayatan lfrewn, fa'iidha rddaha eadat 'iilaa lawnuha alawl, ksayr bdnh"
  7,109,"qal alashraf min qawm frewn: 'iina musaa lasahir yakhudh baeyn alnaas bkhdaeh 'iyahm, hataa yukhayal 'iilayhim 'an aleasa hyt, walshy' bkhlaf ma hu elyh, wahu wasie aleilm balshr mahir bh"
  7,110,"yryd 'an yukhrijakum jmyeana min ardkm, qal frewn: fbmadha tshyrwn ely 'ayuha almala fi 'amr mwsa?"
  7,111,"qal man hadar mnazrt musaa min sadt qawm fireawn wkbrayhm: 'akhkhir musaa wa'akhah harwn, wabeath fi madayin \"msr\" waqalymha alshshurat"
  7,112,lyjmeu lak kl sahir wasie aleilm balshr
  7,113,"wja' alsaharat fireawn qalu: aynn lana lijayizat wmala 'iina ghalabna mwsa?"
  7,114,"qal frewn: nem lakum alajr walqrb miniy 'iina ghalabtumwh"
  7,115,"qal shrt fireawn lmwsa ealaa sabil altkbr wedm almbalat: ya musaa akhtr 'an tulqy easak awla 'aw nulqy nahn awla"
  7,116,"qal musaa llshrt: 'alqawa antm, falamaa alqau alhbal walesy saharuu 'aeyun alnas, fkhuyil 'iilaa al'absar 'ana ma faealuh hqyqt, walam yakun 'iilaa mjrd saneat wkhyal, warhbu alnaas 'irhabana shdydana, wjawu bisihr qawiin kthyr"
  7,117,"wawha allah 'iilaa eabdah warasuluh musaa ealayh alslam fi dhalik almawqif aleazim aldhy frraq allah fih bayn alhaqu walbatl, yamrh bi'ana yulqy ma fi ymynh wahi esah, fa'alqaha fa'iidha hi tble ma ylqwnh, wywhmwn alnaas 'anah haqa wahu batl"
  7,118,"fzhr alhaqu wastban liman shhdh whdrh fi 'amr musaa ealayh alslam, wa'anah rasul allah yadeu 'iilaa alhq, wabatal alkadhib aladhi kanuu yemlwnh"
  7,119,"fghulib jmye alsaharat fi makan ajtmaehm, wansrf fireawn waqawmuh adhla' mqhwryn mghlwbyn"
  7,120,wkharr alsaharat sujjadana ealaa wujuhuhum lilah rabi alealamin lima eaynu min eazim qudrat allh